{
  "id": "y3U444Zp",
  "slug": "croptopia-additions",
  "title": "Croptopia Additions",
  "description": "All the foods you know and love added to Croptopia!",
  "body": "<p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\"><img src=\"https://i.ibb.co/gRsySv4/New-Project-1.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1903\" height=\"818\" data-mce-src=\"https://i.ibb.co/gRsySv4/New-Project-1.png\" data-mce-selected=\"1\"></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Try out my new Cave Overhaul mod, What is Stone!</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/what-is-stone-(colorful-caves)\" data-mce-href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/what-is-stone-(colorful-caves)\">What is 'Stone'? (Colorful Caves)</a></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Like Croptopia, but dislike the boring seed textures?</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Check out my texture pack for Croptopia:</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\"><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/fresh-croptopia-seeds\" data-mce-href=\"https://modrinth.com/resourcepack/fresh-croptopia-seeds\">Fresh Croptopia Seeds</a></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Description</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\">This mod adds several new foods to Minecraft that you can craft using items from Croptopia and a few other mods!&nbsp;</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\">To name a few additions:</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\">- Several flavors of Sodas</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\">- Cotton Candy</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\">- Hot Dogs</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\">- Ramen</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\">- Beans on Toast</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\">And a few more things!</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Yeah, it's a pretty small mod, but it's a starting point for my modding journey. Hmm... If only there was some way I could figure out what to add to this mod...<br></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">That's where you come in!</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Let me know what foods I should add next and/or what the recipe should be in the comments below!</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\">Additionally, you can leave any issues you seem to be having or just features you'd like to see in this mod.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 18px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 18px;\">Other Things</span></p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\">I do plan to update this mod in the future!</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\">If anyone can let me know how to port this mod to Fabric in a somewhat easy manner I'd be glad to do so!</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size: 14px;\" data-mce-style=\"font-size: 14px;\">This mod was made using MCreator. Go check it out here!&nbsp;<a href=\"https://mcreator.net/about\" data-mce-href=\"https://mcreator.net/about\">About MCreator - Minecraft Mod Maker | MCreator</a></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><div id=\"mceResizeHandlenw\" data-mce-bogus=\"all\" class=\"mce-resizehandle\" unselectable=\"true\" data-mce-style=\"cursor: nw-resize; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; left: 4.5px; top: 4.5px;\" style=\"cursor: nw-resize; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; left: 4.5px; top: 4.5px;\"></div><div id=\"mceResizeHandlene\" data-mce-bogus=\"all\" class=\"mce-resizehandle\" unselectable=\"true\" data-mce-style=\"cursor: ne-resize; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; left: 955.5px; top: 4.5px;\" style=\"cursor: ne-resize; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; left: 955.5px; top: 4.5px;\"></div><div id=\"mceResizeHandlese\" data-mce-bogus=\"all\" class=\"mce-resizehandle\" unselectable=\"true\" data-mce-style=\"cursor: se-resize; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; left: 955.5px; top: 413.125px;\" style=\"cursor: se-resize; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; left: 955.5px; top: 413.125px;\"></div><div id=\"mceResizeHandlesw\" data-mce-bogus=\"all\" class=\"mce-resizehandle\" unselectable=\"true\" data-mce-style=\"cursor: sw-resize; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; left: 4.5px; top: 413.125px;\" style=\"cursor: sw-resize; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; left: 4.5px; top: 413.125px;\"></div>",
